StartPage2_Tip1: During free games, 2 additional free spins will be awarded for every 4 wild multipliers symbols appearances
InfoPage1_Tip1: Wild multipliers symbol that appear on reels 2,3,4,5 during a free spin will stay on the reels where they appear until the end of the free games
InfoPage2_Tip1: During free games, 2 additional free spins will be awarded for every 4 wild multipliers symbols appearances
InfoPage3_Tip1:
The wild symbol can replace all symbols except SCATTERl;
the wild symbol will only appear on the 2nd, 3rd, 4th and 5th reels
Every time the wild symbol appears, it is randomly multiplied by X1,
X2 or X3.During payout, if there are one or more wild symbols on the
winning line,  the multiplier will be multiplied during payout
InfoPage3_Tip2:
3 or more bonus symbols appearing on any reel,
will trigger Free Spins
When 3 or more bonus symbols appear,
get 5 times the bet reward
InfoPage3_Tip3:
When 3, 4, or 5 bonus symbols appear, 8, 12,or 16 free spins will be awarded
Wild symbols that appear during a free spin will stay on the reels
where they appear until the end of the free game
When there are more than 4, 8, or 10 wild symbols,
2 additional free games will be given
InfoPage4_Tip1:
No matter in the base game or free game,
when the payout reaches 5000 times,
it will be interrupted and paid immediately
InfoPage4_Tip2:
The FREE SPINS round can be instantly
triggered from the base game by buying it
for 100x the current total bet.
When buying the FREE SPINS
feature, 3,4, or 5 SCATTERS can hit randomly on the triggering screen and 8,12, or 16 freespins will be awarded.
